subject: THANK YOU FOR CONTACTING FEDEX
body:
Attention,

Thank you for contacting FedEx headquarter here in Memphis, Tennessee 38120. we want you to know that your ATM card was deposited here for your delivery, before we proceed you would be advised to get back to us with this information below so we can proceed with your delivery.

Full name :
Address:
Next of kin:
Cell phone #:
Home phone:
Any landmark for description:

Once we confirm all this information we would commence on your delivery, and note that you are advised to also send the fee of $95 first before we can proceed. Your tracking # will be sent to you once the fee is confirmed, you donâ€™t have to delay your parcel here to avoid any demurrage charges.

We need to proceed immediately,

 Yours Faithfully,

Mr. Barry White
